RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MODULE_ID,MODULE_DESC FROM SMTBS_MODULES WHERE MODULE_ID IN ('LB','FC','OL')

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LFTMS_FEE_CCY.BRANCH_CODE = LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY.MODULE = LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.MODULE AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY.COMPONENT = LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.COMPONENT

LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.BRANCH_CODE = LFTMS_FEE_CCY.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.MODULE = LFTMS_FEE_CCY.MODULE AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTMS_FEE_CCY.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_FEE_CCY.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.COMPONENT = LFTMS_FEE_CCY.COMPONENT AND LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.CCY = LFTMS_FEE_CCY.CCY

LFTMS_FEE_RATE.BRANCH_CODE = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_FEE_RATE.MODULE = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.MODULE AND LFTMS_FEE_RATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_RATE.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_RATE.COMPONENT = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.COMPONENT AND LFTMS_FEE_RATE.CCY = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.CCY AND LFTMS_FEE_RATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE = LFTMS_FEE_CCY_EFFDATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.USER_REF_NO, A.BRANCH, X.BOOKING_DATE, X.VALUE_DATE, X.SYNDICATION_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER X WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = X.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND X.VERSION_NO = A.LATEST_VERSION_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = ? AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS <> 'V' AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE LIKE DECODE(?, 'LB', 'C', '%') AND A.MODULE_CODE LIKE NVL(?, '%') AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SMVWS_USER_BRANCHES B WHERE B.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND B.BRANCH_CODE = A.BRANCH) AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH UNION SELECT 'ALL', 'ALL CONTRACTS', 'ALL', NULL, NULL, NULL FROM DUAL

SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO,B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORROWERS A,OLTM_CUSTOMER B WHERE B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL CUSTOMERS' FROM DUAL WHERE ? ='ALL' UNION SELECT B.CUSTOMER_NO,B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTM_CUSTOMER B WHERE 'ALL' = ? UNION SELECT A.COUNTERPARTY, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTM_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY

SELECT A.COMPONENT, A.DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE A WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND NVL(A.STOP_ASSOCIATION, 'N') = 'N' AND COMPONENT IN (SELECT A.FEE_COMPONENT FROM LFTMS_FEE_DEFINITION A WHERE A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O') UNION SELECT A.FEE_COMPONENT, A.DESCRIPTION FROM LFTM_FEE_DEFINITION A WHERE A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND ? = 'ALL' UNION SELECT A.COMPONENT, A.DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE A WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND NVL(A.STOP_ASSOCIATION, 'N') = 'N' AND COMPONENT IN (SELECT A.FEE_COMPONENT FROM LFTM_FEE_DEFINITION A WHERE A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O') AND BASIS_AMOUNT_TAG <> 'USERINPUT' AND A.COMPONENT IN (SELECT DISTINCT D.COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE D WHERE D.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ?) AND ? <> 'ALL'

SELECT A.contract_ccy as CCY_CODE, b.ccy_name as CCY_NAME FROM oltbs_contract A, cytms_ccy_defn b WHERE A.contract_ref_no = ? AND A.contract_ccy = b.ccy_code AND b.record_stat = 'O' AND b.auth_stat = 'A' UNION SELECT A.CCY_CODE, A.CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' and ? = 'ALL'

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.MODULE =LFVW_FEE_COMPONENT_SUMMARY.MODULE AND LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO =LFVW_FEE_COMPONENT_SUMMARY.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.CUSTOMER_NO =LFVW_FEE_COMPONENT_SUMMARY.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.COMPONENT =LFVW_FEE_COMPONENT_SUMMARY.COMPONENT AND LFTMS_FEE_COMPONENT.BRANCH_CODE=LFVW_FEE_COMPONENT_SUMMARY.BRANCH_CODE
